episodes.title: The Irish cult you didn't know about. Meet The Screamers.
episodes.description: The Screamers Irish Cult Episode photos are on our instagram page, comment below to contribute your thoughts.Contact us on instagram if you have a little known Irish or British crime we should cover in future episodes. Me Time & MURDER Instagram: https://www.instagram.com/metimeandmurder/ Sound Effects: Sound Bible: http://soundbible.com/ Episode References:WikipediaLee McDaid - Youtube channel - https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=7Sm-AjNMxco BBC Radio 4 - The Silence and the Scream - https://www.bbc.co.uk/sounds/play/b0bbp9qf
